JF  - Academy of Management Journal
JO  - AMJ
SP  - 221
EP  - 246
VL  - 27
IS  - 2
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - The effectiveness of workgroups should be affected by decisions on technology and structure. Three dimensions of technology, three of structure, and two measures of workgroup effectiveness were used to test a contingency model. Results revealed little support for hypothesized relationships. Several unanticipated significant main and interactive effects of technology on effectiveness were found.
AB  - The effectiveness of workgroups should be affected by decisions on technology and structure. Three dimensions of technology, three of structure, and two measures of workgroup effectiveness were used to test a contingency model. Results revealed little support for hypothesized relationships. Several unanticipated significant main and interactive effects of technology on effectiveness were found.
